<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>198</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. A kumsawt go luoh dingin sem zel hitiu,
 Lungkhamna a hung let lai hin,
 Ka kiengah um zel inla Aw
 Ka hukdampa deih tak,

[V2]
 Aw nawpna gam nuom zuon hitiu,
 Chawlh denna ding
 Aw ka ngai ie khensate,
 Kimna ding gam khu.

[V3]
 2. Lei nawpna tin cheng hi le hung bei ina,
 Tuoi ta puona kumsawt lalna chu,
 Gen zel unau khangthak chanin,
 Agam tawp ta puona.

[V4]
 3. Mita muhloh gam nuom eihaw di'n a siem,
 Zuon zel hitiu awle zie gam chu
 Aw zie mun ngei chu ana hi
 I kumsawt In diu chu.

[V5]
 4. Lei nawpna beikit mai sek muna chengte,
 Kikhen lohna gam ei siemsak ziekin,
 Hallelujah Hukdampa chu,
 Chawihat in um zel hen.</lyrics>
<title>Nawpna Gam Zuon</title>
</song>